## Key Concepts

- [Content Sync](https://dazzle.fm/guide.md#page-setup): Sync a local directory with `index.html` to your stage. `--watch` for live dev. Browser auto-refreshes on sync.
- [Live Events](https://dazzle.fm/guide.md#persistence--live-updates): Push real-time data to running pages via `dazzle s ev e <name> '<json>'` — dispatched as DOM CustomEvents.
- [Persistence](https://dazzle.fm/guide.md#persistence--live-updates): localStorage survives stage restarts via cloud storage.
- [Performance Monitoring](https://dazzle.fm/guide.md#performance-monitoring): `dazzle s stats` for FPS, dropped frames, encoder health. `dazzle s ss` for screenshots.
- [Streaming Destinations](https://dazzle.fm/guide.md): Twitch, YouTube, Kick, Restream, or custom RTMP. Multi-destination simultaneous output.

## Authentication

`dazzle login` opens browser OAuth — no API key needed. For headless/CI use: `export DAZZLE_API_KEY=dzl_your_key_here` (create in dashboard Settings > API Keys).
